Telecom Italia Names Rossetto Head of Consumer Unit, Sole Says

-- B y   C h i a r a   R e m o n d i n i
-- 
2011-04-17T08:50:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-17/telecom-italia-names-rossetto-head-of-consumer-unit-sole-says.html
Telecom Italia SpA (TIT) ,  Italy ’s biggest
phone company, named Luca Rossetto as head of its domestic
consumer unit, daily  Il Sole 24 Ore  reported, without saying
where it got the information.  Rossetto is a former chief executive officer of Upim SpA,
one of the country’s largest department stores, the newspaper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chiara Remondini in Milan at 
 cremondini@bloomberg.net   To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  